name: Self Portrait, December 9, 2021
description:
This work originated from a selfie I took while taking a bath some days ago. Many hours of digital distortion and coloring later, this is what is left of me: A landscape of colors, lines, movements, layers.

My very first NFT on hic.af - 10 editions.

High-quality JPG, 2000x3000 px, approx. 4.54 MB in size.
